at blends well with the rest of the room setup. The loveseat piece also comes with an elastic webbing below the cushion area that gives extra bounce for comfort. It\u2019s the perfect setup to cuddle up with your partner and enjoy a romantic evening.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191823\/wooden-sofa-cum-loveseat.jpg\" alt=\"Two-seat wooden sofa cum loveseat comes with an elastic webbing below the cushion area\" class=\"wp-image-26003\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191823\/wooden-sofa-cum-loveseat.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191823\/wooden-sofa-cum-loveseat-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191823\/wooden-sofa-cum-loveseat-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191823\/wooden-sofa-cum-loveseat-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An All-White Living Room Loveseat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">White never goes wrong! It is classy and ageless. And so is our next loveseat. This white-plain wooden loveseat with high arms is simple and ideal for any living room setting. The exposed wooden legs of the loveseat display a yesteryear\/vintage vibe that is rare and elegant.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191656\/living-room-small-loveseat.jpg\" alt=\"A small loveseat in white colour with high arms is simple and ideal for any living room\" class=\"wp-image-25988\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/10191656\/living-room-small-loveseat.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media